{
    "title": "Processed Meat",
    "screens": [
        {
            "content": [
                {
                    "type": "richtext",
                    "items": [
                        {
                            "text": "Sausages, deli meats, bacon, and prosciutto are examples of",
                            "color": 4280690214
                        },
                        {
                            "text": " processed meats.",
                            "color": 4294923571
                        }
                    ]
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "content": [
                {
                    "type": "richtext",
                    "items": [
                        {
                            "text": "They are delicious and diverse but come with ",
                            "color": 4280690214
                        },
                        {
                            "text": " hidden drawbacks.",
                            "color": 4294923571
                        }
                    ]
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "content": [
                {
                    "type": "richtext",
                    "items": [
                        {
                            "text": "During curing, smoking, or canning, meat often",
                            "color": 4280690214
                        },
                        {
                            "text": " loses its nutritional value.",
                            "color": 4294923571
                        }
                    ]
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "content": [
                {
                    "type": "richtext",
                    "items": [
                        {
                            "text": "Processed meats also contain",
                            "color": 4280690214
                        },
                        {
                            "text": " a lot of salt",
                            "color": 4294923571
                        },
                        {
                            "text": " and are",
                            "color": 4280690214
                        },
                        {
                            "text": " high in fat.",
                            "color": 4294923571
                        }
                    ]
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "content": [
                {
                    "type": "richtext",
                    "items": [
                        {
                            "text": "It is classified as a carcinogen due to the presence of",
                            "color": 4280690214
                        },
                        {
                            "text": " nitrates and nitrites.",
                            "color": 4294923571
                        }
                    ]
                }
            ],
            "link": {
                "title": "World Health Organization",
                "url": "https://www.who.int/news-room/questions-and-answers/item/cancer-carcinogenicity-of-the-consumption-of-red-meat-and-processed-meat"
            }
        },
        {
            "content": [
                {
                    "type": "richtext",
                    "items": [
                        {
                            "text": "Studies have found links between processed meat",
                            "color": 4280690214
                        },
                        {
                            "text": " various forms of cancer",
                            "color": 4294923571
                        },
                        {
                            "text": " as well as",
                            "color": 4280690214
                        },
                        {
                            "text": " heart disease and diabetes.",
                            "color": 4294923571
                        }
                    ]
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "content": [
                {
                    "type": "richtext",
                    "items": [
                        {
                            "text": "This doesn't mean you have to give up processed meats completely – everyone enjoys a hot dog once in a while, right?",
                            "color": 4280690214
                        }
                    ]
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "content": [
                {
                    "type": "richtext",
                    "items": [
                        {
                            "text": "Still, it's best to",
                            "color": 4280690214
                        },
                        {
                            "text": " go easy on them.",
                            "color": 4282888794
                        },
                        {
                            "text": " When possible, choose fish or whole cuts of meat as your main protein source.",
                            "color": 4280690214
                        }
                    ]
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "content": [
                {
                    "type": "richtext",
                    "items": [
                        {
                            "text": "Tips for choosing safer options:",
                            "color": 4280690214
                        }
                    ]
                },
                {
                    "type": "checklist",
                    "items": [
                        {
                            "type": "richtext",
                            "items": [
                                {
                                    "text": "Look for products labeled",
                                    "color": 4280690214
                                },
                                {
                                    "text": " \"reduced sodium\"",
                                    "color": 4282888794
                                }
                            ]
                        },
                        {
                            "type": "richtext",
                            "items": [
                                {
                                    "text": "Choose options that state",
                                    "color": 4280690214
                                },
                                {
                                    "text": " \"no added nitrates or nitrites\"",
                                    "color": 4282888794
                                }
                            ]
                        },
                        {
                            "type": "richtext",
                            "items": [
                                {
                                    "text": "Ensure that the meat’s color",
                                    "color": 4280690214
                                },
                                {
                                    "text": " looks natural,",
                                    "color": 4282888794
                                },
                                {
                                    "text": " not overly bright or artificial",
                                    "color": 4280690214
                                }
                            ]
                        }
                    ]
                }
            ]
        }
    ]
}